@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kbklts(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.36 / (v1 * (v0 + 0.27 + v1 + 0.61)))
    v2 = (v0 + ((tmp + 0.95 - v2 + 0.47) / (tmp + 0.31 * v0 + 0.69)))
    v2 = (0.79 * (0.03 + (v0 + 0.75 + v2 + 0.03)))
    data[tid] = v0
